Promoting Products from the Art Story Project
10 Jul 2023

" NAT Absolute Technologies PCL is committed to promoting and supporting products from the Art Story project, a wonderful showcase of Thai artistic skills. We have purchased these products to distribute at events with our clients, while also helping to promote the Art Story project to encourage support from our colleagues.

 The adorable designs on these products are the creations of children and individuals with autism from the Autistic Thai Foundation. They use their imagination and express their thoughts and emotions through art before transforming them into affordable products. These products are sold under the brand name and project name, "Art Story by Autistic Thai," which has many kind-hearted individuals behind it. The artwork of these children not only helps in their therapy, recovery, and development but also creates sustainable opportunities.

 To further the project's impact, we have taken the artwork of these individuals and developed them into marketable products, generating income and adding value to the lives of children and individuals with autism. The Art Story project is not just about their artwork; it also provides them with stable careers.


 The image shown is from the NT Event, where we showcased products from Art Story as memorable gifts for speakers and important guests."

LET'S SAVE THE EARTH
NAT Absolute Technologies Public Company Limited, has initiated a project to advocate for employees' environmental consciousness regarding emission reduction into the environment. The goal is to encourage employees to be mindful of the environment, starting with simple adjustments in behavior to reduce greenhouse gas emissions from various organizational activities. Our aspiration is to actively contribute to mitigating global warming for the sake of future generations.
More details
Project: Plastic Bottle Caps Initiative
We kindly present the Plastic Bottle Caps Initiative! Project, This initiative aims to deliver plastic bottle caps to support the "Precious Plastic Bangkok" project. Our goal is to contribute to organizations that recycle plastic bottle caps, in order to reduce waste and protect our planet.
More details
FEED X MATICHON TV GOLF CHARITY 2022
NAT Absolute Technologies PCL (formerly known as NAT Consulting Co., Ltd.) proudly participated in the FEED X MATICHON TV GOLF CHARITY 2022 event on December 14, 2565. As part of our commitment to social responsibility, a portion of the proceeds, after deducting expenses, was donated to the Mirror Foundation - Home for Disabled Animals.
